Hover-on-parent action as in baobab

    When the user hovers the mouse over a process wedge long enough, the
    titles of the major children of that process should appear (if space
    is available).

There should be an update graph button to regenerate the graph.

Process name wrapping

    Currently, the edges of the chart can cut off process names.

    https://stackoverflow.com/questions/4018860/text-box-in-matplotlib may be
    useful.

Optimize wedge mouse hover detection

    70% cpu usage when moving the mouse over the window quickly on a netbook
